WEBVTT

00:03:28.569 --> 00:03:31.242
because they're fighting
a war in their head

00:03:31.266 --> 00:03:32.809
that nobody else can see.

00:03:33.307 --> 00:03:34.529
On the other side,

00:03:36.074 --> 00:03:39.057
the vast majority of people
look across the chasm

00:03:39.081 --> 00:03:40.232
and shake their heads,

00:03:40.256 --> 00:03:43.272
like, "Why you gotta be so depressed?"

00:03:44.817 --> 00:03:48.457
You may recognize
a divide like this in your life.

00:03:49.066 --> 00:03:51.055
Do you want to build a bridge across it?

00:03:51.712 --> 00:03:53.856
You may not want to build a bridge --

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:56.475
and that's a totally valid choice.

00:03:57.182 --> 00:04:00.660
Or maybe you'd like to build
a stronger connection,